    <item>
      <title>由于沙特阿拉伯提高价格，油价在每周暴跌后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在一周下跌后上涨，原因是沙特阿拉伯对亚洲客户的价格上涨表明了对前景的信心，而以色列在加沙地带的最新举动使人们重新关注该地区的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 23:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国习近平抵达巴黎，法国加大电动汽车雄心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/france-ramps-up-electric-vehicle-ambition-as-xi-arrives-in-paris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府周一与汽车行业签署了一项内容广泛的协议，为电动汽车销售设定了新目标，恰逢中国国家主席习近平抵达该行业进行国事访问，该行业的贸易紧张局势笼罩着阴云。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/france-ramps-up-electric-vehicle-ambition-as-xi-arrives-in-paris</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
